with your anxieties right now.

22:53.120 --> 22:56.580
I promise you, not all men cheat.

22:57.660 --> 22:58.660
I know.

22:58.750 --> 23:03.170
And you have two more babies on the way.
It's a very stressful time.

23:03.840 --> 23:07.840
Oh, my God, I forgot there were two.

23:07.920 --> 23:10.050
-Oh, jeez.
-Oh.

23:19.060 --> 23:20.270
Oh!

23:20.350 --> 23:24.190
-Ahha! Ooh!
