25:30.110 --> 25:31.110
You OK?

25:31.190 --> 25:35.200
It's getting to be time
for the pudding, puddin'.

25:35.280 --> 25:37.870
-OK, I'll be right back.
-Where are you going?

25:38.990 --> 25:40.870
I'm gonna get the pudding, puddin'.

25:47.290 --> 25:48.920
Oh! Frankie.

25:49.000 --> 25:51.380
