27:55.540 --> 27:59.510
It's a little bit... overwhelming.

28:01.430 --> 28:03.010
I love you all.

28:03.090 --> 28:06.180
Now get the hell out of my house.

28:14.650 --> 28:15.480
Babe...

28:16.230 --> 28:18.030
Oopsie.

28:18.110 --> 28:20.030
