could be right around the corner.

28:33.290 --> 28:37.090
I don't need a miracle, sugar.
I've had a really good ride.

28:37.170 --> 28:42.630
I've lived it hard and well.
With every breath, right?

28:42.720 --> 28:45.840
Inhale peace, exhale joy.

28:45.930 --> 28:49.390
Inhale peace, exhale joy.

28:49.470 --> 28:51.600
